WEBVTT

00:16.320 --> 00:17.850
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:18.350 --> 00:19.750
Please get up, Madam Liu.

00:24.640 --> 00:26.350
I'd hoped you'd spend
the rest of your lives in peace.

00:26.350 --> 00:27.150
But in the end,

00:27.550 --> 00:29.880
I still dragged you into this deadly game.

00:30.600 --> 00:32.729
We're at your command, Your Highness.

00:33.350 --> 00:36.210
How many people can we call on
in Jiankang right now?

00:36.280 --> 00:38.070
Twenty-seven are still alive.

00:38.880 --> 00:40.080
How many are under 60?

00:40.240 --> 00:41.030
Eleven.

00:41.840 --> 00:43.350
But those who can still fight

00:43.350 --> 00:44.520
are 27.

00:46.000 --> 00:47.000
We're old,

00:47.600 --> 00:49.200
but we can still hold a sword.

00:54.320 --> 00:55.600
Aside from us,

00:56.240 --> 00:57.470
these are all the people we can mobilize

00:57.470 --> 00:58.670
within Jiankang.

00:59.430 --> 01:01.070
We can also make use of the tunnels

01:01.070 --> 01:02.030
and waterways.

01:03.030 --> 01:05.069
Tomorrow, we'll surely help Your Highness

01:05.069 --> 01:07.270
rescue Prince Jing'an and your family.

02:37.100 --> 02:40.920
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

02:41.310 --> 02:43.900
[Episode 25]

03:22.410 --> 03:24.150
Wuyi, don't dwell on it.

03:25.400 --> 03:27.310
You've done your utmost for Li Mao,

03:27.310 --> 03:29.710
yet he's the one
who insists on wiping us all out.

03:29.710 --> 03:32.240
So we don't need to
suffer in silence anymore.

03:32.240 --> 03:34.150
Once we rescue Father and Mother tomorrow

03:34.150 --> 03:35.590
and make it out of Jiankang

03:35.590 --> 03:36.920
to the Northern Border,

03:37.240 --> 03:39.300
he won't be able to do anything to you.

03:42.000 --> 03:44.329
Once again, I'm dragging you into danger.

03:45.400 --> 03:47.800
I'm afraid things won't
end well this time.

03:50.310 --> 03:52.040
If anything happens tomorrow,

03:52.470 --> 03:53.030
Yaoyao,

03:53.680 --> 03:54.810
you must stay alive.

03:56.870 --> 03:57.470
Remember—

03:58.520 --> 03:59.590
no matter what happens,

03:59.590 --> 04:00.850
you have to stay alive.

04:04.080 --> 04:04.810
Don't worry.

04:05.710 --> 04:07.190
Even including all of us,

04:07.190 --> 04:09.190
we're only a little over 30 in total.

04:09.280 --> 04:10.030
But they all look

04:10.030 --> 04:11.560
utterly loyal and capable.

04:11.910 --> 04:12.540
Look,

04:12.840 --> 04:14.750
even though you gave them free rein
for over 20 years,

04:14.750 --> 04:16.000
they still managed to build

04:16.000 --> 04:17.800
such an extensive network here.

04:18.630 --> 04:20.089
With their help tomorrow,

04:20.390 --> 04:21.950
even if we can't win in a head-on fight,

04:21.950 --> 04:23.040
we should be able to

04:23.390 --> 04:25.650
create enough chaos to rescue everyone.

04:28.120 --> 04:28.800
Yaoyao.

04:32.430 --> 04:33.070
I'm sorry.

04:35.600 --> 04:37.000
Why are you apologizing?

04:39.270 --> 04:41.750
This time, Yuanji even got punished
because of us.

04:41.750 --> 04:43.600
But she was the top scholar
of the Spring Examination—

04:43.600 --> 04:46.360
the very model Li Mao uses
to win over scholars throughout the realm.

04:46.360 --> 04:48.630
Even if Li Mao is displeased
that she spoke out,

04:48.630 --> 04:50.560
I don't think he'll truly harm her.

05:08.630 --> 05:09.290
Go to sleep.

05:12.580 --> 05:13.140
You...

05:13.760 --> 05:14.290
I...

05:20.190 --> 05:21.720
How could I possibly sleep?

05:21.950 --> 05:23.950
Tomorrow is a battle of life and death.

05:23.950 --> 05:26.270
This is the last peaceful night
we'll ever have.

05:26.270 --> 05:27.130
Go to sleep now.

05:41.390 --> 05:42.240
Mother,

05:42.630 --> 05:44.310
why were you spanked?

05:45.630 --> 05:47.240
Did you do something wrong?

05:47.800 --> 05:48.870
When you grow up,

05:49.600 --> 05:52.600
you don't only get spanked
for doing something wrong.

05:53.000 --> 05:54.530
Sometimes, you get spanked

05:55.040 --> 05:56.700
for doing the right thing too.

05:58.560 --> 05:59.950
That's so unfair.

06:00.630 --> 06:03.310
I'd better not grow up then.

06:10.560 --> 06:11.510
Mother,

06:11.750 --> 06:13.950
how is the plague outside?

06:14.070 --> 06:15.800
Are Mama Ruisheng and Father

06:15.870 --> 06:17.310
doing well?

06:17.480 --> 06:19.140
I've finished all the lessons

06:19.270 --> 06:20.600
Mama left for me.

06:21.310 --> 06:23.270
But she still hasn't come to pick me up.

06:23.270 --> 06:24.820
I miss her.

06:27.160 --> 06:28.620
There's a plague outside?

06:28.630 --> 06:30.390
Chan told me

06:30.390 --> 06:33.050
Grandfather and Grandmother
had both caught it

06:33.240 --> 06:36.120
and that we had to hide in the palace
to be safe.

06:36.310 --> 06:38.230
Have they recovered yet?

06:39.159 --> 06:41.090
A plague doesn't end that quickly.

06:42.630 --> 06:44.800
Young Master Xiao,
please rest easy in the palace.

06:44.800 --> 06:46.360
Tomorrow, your father

06:46.360 --> 06:47.870
will come into the palace to be with you.

06:47.870 --> 06:49.430
What about my mama, Ruisheng?

06:49.430 --> 06:51.510
Your mama is a physician.

06:51.830 --> 06:53.190
There are so many sick people outside.

06:53.190 --> 06:54.950
She has to treat them, right?

06:56.270 --> 06:59.000
Young Master Xiao,
take good care of your mother.

06:59.000 --> 07:01.360
I'm sure
your family will be reunited soon.

07:01.360 --> 07:04.890
These are the sugar cakes
His Highness made especially for you.

07:10.830 --> 07:12.480
So this is how you've been fooling him.

07:12.480 --> 07:13.510
His Highness said

07:13.920 --> 07:14.960
grown-up matters

07:15.310 --> 07:17.510
aren't something a child needs to know.

07:18.000 --> 07:19.040
You just said

07:19.830 --> 07:22.240
Young Lord Xiao would enter
the palace tomorrow.

07:22.240 --> 07:23.370
What does that mean?

07:23.480 --> 07:25.630
We heard Young Lord Xiao
has already entered the city.

07:25.630 --> 07:28.120
His Highness fears
he may have caught the plague outside

07:28.120 --> 07:30.000
and plans to invite him and the others
to the palace tomorrow

07:30.000 --> 07:32.330
to visit Prince Jing'an and the Princess.

07:34.210 --> 07:36.620
Is Xiao Yao sick too?

07:38.040 --> 07:39.360
Is he dying as well?

07:39.630 --> 07:40.310
Lady He,

07:41.159 --> 07:42.870
it hasn't been easy for you
to get where you are today.

07:42.870 --> 07:44.920
His Highness has given you a place
to prove yourself.

07:44.920 --> 07:47.270
Don't throw away his goodwill
for the sake of people

07:47.270 --> 07:49.000
who have nothing to do with you.

07:51.870 --> 07:53.310
Attend to them carefully.

07:53.310 --> 07:54.680
Don't let Lady He and Young Master Xiao

07:54.680 --> 07:57.000
come into contact with anyone from outside
and catch the plague.

07:57.000 --> 07:57.680
Yes.

08:16.230 --> 08:17.960
The execution ground is ready?

08:19.190 --> 08:19.830
Good.

08:22.600 --> 08:24.730
Tomorrow, I'll let the whole world see

08:25.870 --> 08:28.730
just what kind of loyal subject
Xiao Wuyi really is.

09:25.550 --> 09:26.360
Three,

09:27.420 --> 09:28.230
two,

09:29.390 --> 09:29.960
one.

09:37.600 --> 09:38.330
Go save them!

10:18.910 --> 10:20.360
That's the execution drum.

10:20.360 --> 10:21.960
We've been tricked by Li Mao!

10:22.670 --> 10:23.270
Xiao Wuyi!

10:24.720 --> 10:26.000
There's no time. Go save them quickly.

10:26.000 --> 10:26.930
Leave this to us.

10:27.390 --> 10:28.850
Qing Long, protect Jiayu.

10:28.910 --> 10:29.360
Yes.

10:31.200 --> 10:31.860
Be careful.

10:34.670 --> 10:35.840
Madam Liu, let's go.

10:42.670 --> 10:43.400
Stand aside.

10:46.550 --> 10:48.480
If Your Highness repents,

10:49.480 --> 10:51.480
you may yet have a chance to survive.

10:57.030 --> 11:02.720
Kill him!

11:26.390 --> 11:27.850
You're all citizens of Ye.

11:29.240 --> 11:31.370
I don't want to see your blood spilled.

11:51.220 --> 11:56.490
♪ Fight to the bitter end ♪

11:56.510 --> 12:00.100
♪ My promises endure like a river ♪

12:00.120 --> 12:03.040
♪ I dare you to challenge me ♪

12:03.080 --> 12:06.190
♪ Listen, the winds begin to roar ♪

12:06.210 --> 12:08.890
♪ The clash of arms rages on ♪

12:08.920 --> 12:10.740
♪ Let flames
sweep the plains in darkness ♪

12:10.760 --> 12:14.390
♪ Still hot-blooded ♪

12:14.420 --> 12:18.460
♪ Fight and let flames
sweep the plains in darkness ♪

12:19.050 --> 12:21.980
♪ Still hot-blooded ♪

12:22.650 --> 12:25.410
♪ My heart stays true ♪

12:25.430 --> 12:30.340
♪ Fight to the bitter end ♪

12:30.560 --> 12:35.930
♪ My promises endure like a river ♪

12:36.410 --> 12:40.220
♪ I dare you ♪

13:07.390 --> 13:08.200
Xiao Wuyi,

13:09.390 --> 13:11.390
is this what you call

13:12.030 --> 13:14.230
serving the nation with all your heart?

13:16.030 --> 13:18.630
Prince Jing'an Xiao Ju
framed loyal officials

13:18.790 --> 13:20.360
and fabricated a miscarriage of justice,

13:20.360 --> 13:23.320
endangering the fate of the nation
and leading to the fall of the Capital.

13:23.320 --> 13:24.600
His intent violates the law,

13:24.600 --> 13:26.530
and his crimes warrant execution.

13:26.600 --> 13:28.490
Yet today, in broad daylight,

13:29.390 --> 13:30.750
you slaughter the Imperial Guards

13:30.750 --> 13:32.550
and storm the execution ground.

13:32.590 --> 13:34.550
Where does that leave the law of the land?

13:34.550 --> 13:37.010
Where does that
leave justice for the realm?

13:37.120 --> 13:38.120
Heaven's principles are clear,

13:38.120 --> 13:39.390
and the law of the land
cannot tolerate this.

13:39.390 --> 13:43.080
If the entire Jing'an household
is not brought to justice today,

13:44.270 --> 13:45.870
how can I answer to the realm?

13:46.150 --> 13:47.720
And how can I uphold
the order of the state?

13:47.720 --> 13:48.270
Li Mao!

13:50.120 --> 13:51.380
I've already given you

13:51.510 --> 13:52.840
everything you wanted.

13:55.200 --> 13:56.400
Except for one thing.

13:56.720 --> 13:58.270
What exactly do you want?

14:01.480 --> 14:03.360
A just cause.

14:16.220 --> 14:17.980
I'm giving you one last chance.

14:19.180 --> 14:20.110
Let my family go.

14:20.840 --> 14:22.600
I am the Regent of the realm.

14:23.270 --> 14:24.720
Are you trying to rebel?

14:27.390 --> 14:29.540
His Majesty's imperial edict!

14:33.140 --> 14:34.750
I rule all under heaven and uphold

14:34.750 --> 14:36.140
the virtue of wise governance.

14:36.140 --> 14:38.720
The truth of the An-Lu wrongful case
has been revealed.

14:38.720 --> 14:39.790
Prince Jing'an Xiao Ju

14:39.790 --> 14:42.270
harbored malicious intentions
and framed loyal subjects.

14:42.270 --> 14:44.720
Today, the Xiao family
has been brought to justice.

14:44.720 --> 14:47.480
I hereby order Xiao Wuyi to surrender
and confess immediately.

14:47.480 --> 14:48.680
Do not disappoint me,

14:48.870 --> 14:52.470
and do not let the people of the realm
suffer further from the war.

14:54.790 --> 14:55.990
Beifu Black Cavalry,

14:56.940 --> 14:59.200
seize the criminal Xiao Wuyi at once.

15:05.240 --> 15:07.030
Do you really think my Beifu soldiers

15:07.030 --> 15:08.490
will take orders from you?

15:10.390 --> 15:11.520
Then let's find out.

15:11.920 --> 15:13.050
Seize the criminal!

15:15.200 --> 15:16.660
Isn't this moment ironic?

15:17.440 --> 15:18.510
You once poured your heart and soul

15:18.510 --> 15:20.390
into pushing through the Beifu Reform,

15:20.390 --> 15:22.750
even going so far as to turn
the private army loyal to you and your clan

15:22.750 --> 15:24.440
into an army for the nation.

15:24.790 --> 15:26.320
What courage.

15:26.510 --> 15:27.630
What vision.

15:28.000 --> 15:29.600
But I doubt you ever imagined

15:29.750 --> 15:31.910
that the very army you built
with such devotion

15:31.910 --> 15:32.960
would one day

15:33.440 --> 15:35.000
turn on you

15:35.320 --> 15:36.750
and take your life.

15:37.080 --> 15:38.200
Mao, you...

15:41.790 --> 15:42.600
Execute!

15:52.520 --> 15:53.160
Brother!

16:39.670 --> 16:40.870
Let my family go.

17:11.240 --> 17:12.030
Let go of me!

17:12.310 --> 17:13.400
You... Let go...

17:15.619 --> 17:16.220
Xiao Wuyi!

17:18.640 --> 17:20.109
Give Yaoyao back to me...

17:20.230 --> 17:20.990
Xiao Wuyi!

17:21.920 --> 17:22.550
Let go!

17:22.960 --> 17:24.240
Li Mao, you lunatic!

17:24.240 --> 17:25.569
Tell them to let go of me!

17:26.510 --> 17:27.349
Xiao Wuyi!

17:38.070 --> 17:38.680
Li Mao!

17:39.680 --> 17:40.880
Li Mao, you're crazy!

17:40.920 --> 17:41.760
Let go of me!

17:41.920 --> 17:42.550
Xiao Wuyi,

17:43.230 --> 17:44.160
with this arrow,

17:44.450 --> 17:45.450
we're even!

17:46.310 --> 17:47.230
Li Mao, you're crazy!

17:47.230 --> 17:47.860
Kill them!

17:48.640 --> 17:49.310
Don't kill my father.

17:49.310 --> 17:49.840
Execute!

17:52.880 --> 17:53.510
No!

18:24.640 --> 18:25.350
Father...

18:26.550 --> 18:27.270
Mother...

18:32.070 --> 18:32.720
Li Mao.

18:35.120 --> 18:36.710
I will make you pay for this.

18:39.640 --> 18:40.550
Xiao Wuyi!

18:48.720 --> 18:49.350
Yaoyao...

19:35.680 --> 19:36.810
Capture the traitor

19:37.590 --> 19:38.790
and kill the rebels!

19:43.200 --> 19:44.790
Qing Long, Yan Yue, protect the Heir!

19:44.790 --> 19:47.680
Kill them!

19:49.000 --> 19:50.930
Bring Xie Jiayu back to the palace.

19:57.200 --> 19:58.060
Your Highness!

19:58.400 --> 19:59.070
Xiao Wuyi!

20:18.880 --> 20:20.750
Your Highness, we're safe now.

20:21.270 --> 20:22.330
Where should we go?

20:22.880 --> 20:24.940
Let's go back to the Northern Border.

20:25.270 --> 20:26.730
There's mist. Be careful.

20:30.160 --> 20:30.790
Yan Yue!

21:55.920 --> 21:57.380
You haven't eaten in days.

21:57.750 --> 21:58.920
Whatever you want to say,

21:58.920 --> 22:00.380
say it after you've eaten.

22:07.240 --> 22:07.830
Yaoyao,

22:08.830 --> 22:09.960
you once told me that

22:10.680 --> 22:12.680
even if Xiao Wuyi died before you,

22:13.310 --> 22:14.830
as long as he had never betrayed you

22:14.830 --> 22:15.790
or let you down,

22:16.790 --> 22:18.990
you would still carry on living for him.

22:20.030 --> 22:20.760
Come on, eat.

22:24.790 --> 22:26.850
Are you going to keep me here forever?

22:27.400 --> 22:29.350
You should know what I'm capable of.

22:29.350 --> 22:30.680
No lock in this world

22:31.350 --> 22:32.270
can hold me.

22:40.550 --> 22:41.720
Locks can't hold you,

22:41.720 --> 22:42.680
but poison can.

22:43.550 --> 22:44.880
Muscle-Weakening Powder.

22:44.880 --> 22:46.550
At least it'll make sure
you can't go anywhere,

22:46.550 --> 22:48.210
so we can get married in peace.

22:48.880 --> 22:50.480
You might as well kill me now!

22:52.950 --> 22:54.720
Otherwise, as long as I'm alive,

22:54.720 --> 22:55.880
I'll avenge Xiao Wuyi!

22:55.880 --> 22:58.280
You already stabbed me
with a hairpin once.

22:59.770 --> 23:00.970
Xiao Wuyi isn't dead.

23:02.550 --> 23:03.680
He escaped the city.

23:06.160 --> 23:07.400
When he fled,

23:08.200 --> 23:09.530
he was heavily injured.

23:09.830 --> 23:12.160
I'd already laid an ambush
outside the city.

23:12.160 --> 23:13.790
Yet the moment he got out,

23:14.920 --> 23:16.400
someone rescued him.

23:17.480 --> 23:18.070
Tell me,

23:19.110 --> 23:20.160
who saved him?

23:21.000 --> 23:23.330
Does he still have hidden private troops?

23:24.720 --> 23:26.580
Looks like you don't know either.

23:26.750 --> 23:27.510
Xie Jiayu,

23:28.490 --> 23:30.490
it seems he never truly trusted you.

23:33.350 --> 23:34.750
Bad news, Your Highness!

23:35.920 --> 23:36.520
Insolent!

23:37.110 --> 23:39.030
How dare you barge in
without announcing yourself?

23:39.030 --> 23:40.240
Forgive me, Your Highness.

23:40.240 --> 23:42.100
I have an urgent matter to report.

23:42.160 --> 23:42.750
Speak.

23:44.270 --> 23:45.930
Xiao... Xiao Ziqi is missing.

23:46.750 --> 23:48.830
After knocking out
Miss Chan with acupuncture,

23:48.830 --> 23:49.590
he ran away.

23:50.340 --> 23:51.940
He is nowhere to be found now.

23:52.200 --> 23:53.210
Search the palace and find him now!

23:53.210 --> 23:53.650
Yes.

24:09.590 --> 24:11.200
When you see Grand Tutor Xie later,

24:11.200 --> 24:11.800
don't cry.

24:12.510 --> 24:13.740
Death wipes the slate clean.

24:13.740 --> 24:16.000
Don't hold a grudge against him anymore.

24:18.550 --> 24:19.240
Execute!

24:20.680 --> 24:21.510
Brother!

24:22.590 --> 24:23.790
Xiao Ziqi is missing.

24:26.590 --> 24:28.520
Search the palace and find him now!

24:34.070 --> 24:35.730
In my first year in the palace,

24:35.750 --> 24:38.410
I, too, often stood here alone,
deep in thought.

24:39.070 --> 24:39.830
I'd wonder

24:41.720 --> 24:43.960
what you and Wuyi were doing

24:44.960 --> 24:46.090
outside the palace.

24:47.240 --> 24:48.370
At first, I imagined

24:50.000 --> 24:50.640
you were probably blowing up

24:50.640 --> 24:52.570
the alchemy furnace again at home,

24:54.030 --> 24:56.630
while Wuyi might be off
at the Northern Border,

24:57.270 --> 24:58.830
where swords clash and battles rage.

24:58.830 --> 25:00.690
But the longer I thought about it,

25:01.160 --> 25:03.720
the fewer images of you I could conjure.

25:06.270 --> 25:07.240
Until one day,

25:09.770 --> 25:11.900
I couldn't picture you at all anymore.

25:14.030 --> 25:14.920
Years later,

25:15.680 --> 25:17.410
I came back here again to think.

25:18.640 --> 25:19.480
I wondered

25:21.310 --> 25:23.200
what we would have done together

25:26.110 --> 25:28.370
if you had stayed in the palace back then.

25:30.480 --> 25:32.080
I thought about it for a long,

25:32.590 --> 25:33.350
long time.

25:34.590 --> 25:37.050
But I couldn't come up with
a single scenario

25:38.000 --> 25:40.330
where you'd be happy,
and I'd be happy too.

25:40.680 --> 25:42.210
Yet just now, I understood.

25:46.270 --> 25:48.670
Just having you stand quietly
by my side...

25:51.110 --> 25:52.000
is enough.

25:58.240 --> 25:59.970
Now my wish has been fulfilled.

26:00.920 --> 26:01.720
There are

26:03.110 --> 26:04.910
no more regrets left between us.

26:08.480 --> 26:10.340
You seem very worried about Ziqi.

26:10.640 --> 26:11.480
Why would you, Prince Qi,

26:11.480 --> 26:13.340
who drove Xiao Wuyi into a corner,

26:13.350 --> 26:14.200
care so much

26:14.200 --> 26:15.930
about an insignificant child?

26:16.880 --> 26:18.740
Are you hiding something from me?

26:19.750 --> 26:20.680
We've found him!

26:23.440 --> 26:24.210
Your Highness,

26:24.210 --> 26:26.350
Eunuch Feng has found Young Master Xiao.

26:26.350 --> 26:27.410
Give me your hands.

26:30.620 --> 26:31.720
Aren't you afraid I'll run away too?

26:31.720 --> 26:32.690
If you were to run,

26:32.690 --> 26:34.620
you'd surely find Xiao Ziqi first.

26:35.000 --> 26:35.530
Let's go.

26:39.440 --> 26:40.300
Little master.

26:40.790 --> 26:42.390
Little master, please stop.

26:42.680 --> 26:43.480
Come on, let's go.

26:43.480 --> 26:43.920
Stop playing.

26:43.920 --> 26:44.960
Let go of me!

26:45.030 --> 26:46.250
I want to find my mama!

26:46.400 --> 26:47.110
You're all liars!

26:47.110 --> 26:47.550
Alright, alright.

26:47.550 --> 26:49.410
There is no plague outside at all!

26:49.590 --> 26:51.400
Auntie, help!

26:51.640 --> 26:53.070
They're all bad people!

26:53.480 --> 26:55.200
They beat Mother!

26:55.200 --> 26:57.240
-Mama is missing.
-Young Master Xiao.

26:57.240 --> 26:58.830
They're all bad people!

26:59.030 --> 27:01.000
Bad people! You big villain!

27:01.060 --> 27:02.430
You killed my grandfather and grandmother!

27:02.430 --> 27:04.680
-Alright.
-You even want to kill my father too!

27:04.680 --> 27:05.440
Feng An,

27:05.890 --> 27:07.440
take him back to the Eastern Palace.

27:07.440 --> 27:08.570
If he escapes again,

27:09.000 --> 27:10.510
you'll answer for it yourself.

27:10.510 --> 27:11.640
Yes, Your Highness.

27:11.970 --> 27:12.830
Let's go. Come on.

27:12.830 --> 27:14.400
Let's go. Come on.

27:17.720 --> 27:18.240
Hurry.

27:26.480 --> 27:28.400
Stay put.

27:29.590 --> 27:30.160
Da,

27:30.160 --> 27:31.480
next time you want me to stay put,

27:31.480 --> 27:32.940
just use this hand signal.

27:35.910 --> 27:36.390
Right.

27:56.920 --> 27:58.120
Xiao Wuyi isn't dead.

27:58.680 --> 27:59.810
He escaped the city.

28:04.680 --> 28:05.240
Mao,

28:06.070 --> 28:08.530
that letter you didn't get a chance
to give me

28:09.200 --> 28:10.330
is from Wuyi, right?

28:13.030 --> 28:13.790
Give it to me.

28:14.720 --> 28:15.650
How did you know?

28:16.480 --> 28:18.140
From the way you treated Ziqi.

28:18.880 --> 28:20.920
How could someone
who slaughtered innocent people

28:20.920 --> 28:23.920
at the execution ground
be so concerned about a child?

28:24.200 --> 28:24.830
Unless

28:25.750 --> 28:26.790
it's all an act.

28:28.960 --> 28:31.000
So I went back over everything
that's happened

28:31.000 --> 28:32.130
these past few days,

28:33.350 --> 28:35.680
along with the hand signal
Da just gave me.

28:37.350 --> 28:38.880
And these medicinal herbs.

28:39.440 --> 28:40.900
I was already 90% certain.

28:42.270 --> 28:43.310
These precious herbs

28:43.310 --> 28:44.880
are all used to treat blood stasis.

28:44.880 --> 28:46.610
If you truly meant to kill Wuyi,

28:47.720 --> 28:50.720
why would you have someone
brew medicine for him here?

28:53.680 --> 28:55.080
What about the other 10%?

28:57.030 --> 28:57.890
I was bluffing.

29:00.200 --> 29:02.060
How do you recognize these herbs?

29:03.640 --> 29:04.790
I taught her.

29:07.640 --> 29:09.350
Prince Qi sought out the miraculous doctor

29:09.350 --> 29:10.350
to treat the Heir.

29:17.030 --> 29:18.290
You knew all along too?

29:18.750 --> 29:19.830
Then how is Xiao Wuyi now...

29:19.830 --> 29:21.960
As long as that arrow struck
exactly where it was meant to,

29:21.960 --> 29:23.360
his life is not in danger.

29:27.160 --> 29:28.240
As for the blood stasis,

29:28.240 --> 29:29.510
the miraculous doctor has prepared pills.

29:29.510 --> 29:30.880
They can at least keep the Heir stable

29:30.880 --> 29:31.750
for 2 months.

29:38.400 --> 29:40.060
Da's men are all trustworthy.

29:43.400 --> 29:44.130
Give it to me.

30:03.200 --> 30:04.330
"My dear wife Jiayu,

30:04.830 --> 30:06.690
I hope this letter finds you well.

30:07.160 --> 30:08.590
I told Yizhi that once he confirmed

30:08.590 --> 30:10.750
I'd been captured by Northern Qin spies,

30:10.750 --> 30:12.610
he should tell you the whole truth

30:13.270 --> 30:15.400
to spare you prolonged fear and grief.

30:16.790 --> 30:18.920
But you must have already cried by now.

30:19.630 --> 30:20.740
The thought of this

30:21.270 --> 30:22.640
unsettles my heart.

30:24.270 --> 30:24.960
Yaoyao,

30:26.270 --> 30:29.000
I, Xiao Wuyi, have never failed anyone
in my life,

30:29.550 --> 30:30.550
except you.

30:32.310 --> 30:35.270
Perhaps this will be
my final letter in this lifetime.

30:35.270 --> 30:39.330
Even so, I still want to start from
where it all began: Crown Prince Wenxi.

30:42.270 --> 30:43.510
Before I turned 13,

30:44.440 --> 30:46.400
I believed my fate
would be the same as Father's

30:46.400 --> 30:48.250
and all my uncles'—

30:48.790 --> 30:50.640
to become a commander
of the Imperial Guards,

30:50.640 --> 30:53.300
protecting the palace
and the imperial throne.

30:54.270 --> 30:56.400
But then Northern Qin invaded Qizhou.

30:56.760 --> 30:59.420
That was the first time
I saw a real battlefield.

31:00.000 --> 31:03.060
It was also the first time
I learned of my true identity.

31:03.240 --> 31:04.840
One hundred and forty-seven

31:04.960 --> 31:07.690
Shadow Envoys
sacrificed their lives to save me.

31:13.390 --> 31:16.220
[Xiao Sheng]

31:14.780 --> 31:16.780
From now on, your name is Xiao Sheng.

31:18.070 --> 31:19.870
From today on, he is your master.

31:20.880 --> 31:22.240
Greetings, Your Highness.

31:21.260 --> 31:24.700
[Young Qing Long; Young Yan Yue]

31:22.720 --> 31:23.580
He's Qing Long.

31:23.880 --> 31:24.790
She's Yan Yue.

31:25.030 --> 31:27.360
From now on,
they will remain by your side.

31:29.440 --> 31:31.000
"I held the Phoenix Heart Token,

31:31.000 --> 31:31.890
and the expectation that
'when the Phoenix Heart Token appears,

31:31.890 --> 31:33.790
peace shall be restored in the world.'

31:33.790 --> 31:35.790
Yet in my heart, I felt utterly lost.

31:36.270 --> 31:37.000
If the infamous An-Lu treason case

31:37.000 --> 31:38.550
that shook the entire realm

31:38.550 --> 31:39.940
were truly a miscarriage of justice,

31:39.940 --> 31:42.130
and my parents were the root cause

31:42.270 --> 31:44.440
of the Capital's fall and 20 years of war,

31:44.440 --> 31:45.680
could I really, with just a single token,

31:45.680 --> 31:46.750
command all under heaven

31:46.750 --> 31:48.350
and bring peace to the realm?

31:49.750 --> 31:51.720
Are the elite troops of Ye meant only to
fight for the powerful and noble...

31:51.720 --> 31:52.920
It was only after I met Yizhi...

31:52.920 --> 31:54.030
Not for the common people?

31:54.030 --> 31:55.030
That I found my direction.

31:55.030 --> 31:56.880
It wasn't wrong
for Emperor Wenxi and the Empress

31:56.880 --> 31:59.070
to support commoner officials
in order to check the noble clans.

31:59.070 --> 32:01.030
They simply chose the wrong time

32:01.270 --> 32:02.550
and failed to keep the right balance.

32:02.550 --> 32:05.000
That gave Northern Qin
the opening it needed.

32:05.000 --> 32:06.830
Then what, in your view,
is the right time,

32:06.830 --> 32:08.830
and how should that balance be kept?

32:09.440 --> 32:10.570
The past is the past,

32:10.750 --> 32:11.830
and now is now.

32:12.240 --> 32:13.700
We are now in a chaotic age,

32:13.750 --> 32:15.790
and a chaotic age calls for harsh laws.

32:15.790 --> 32:16.990
Thank you. Your words

32:17.160 --> 32:18.510
have enlightened me.

32:25.830 --> 32:26.750
Ye needs an army

32:26.750 --> 32:29.410
that truly fights for
the people and the nation.

32:30.200 --> 32:31.860
Compared to Jiankang Palace,

32:31.920 --> 32:34.120
I belonged more on the Northern Border.

32:37.030 --> 32:38.030
Eight years of war

32:38.880 --> 32:40.140
gave Ye the Beifu Army,

32:40.790 --> 32:42.590
and Xiao Sheng became Xiao Wuyi.

32:44.480 --> 32:45.640
Yizhi was right.

32:46.350 --> 32:48.750
If I hadn't been gravely wounded
at Jiuzhang Plain,

32:48.750 --> 32:50.550
perhaps I might eventually have

32:50.550 --> 32:52.080
become Crown Prince Wenxi.

32:54.350 --> 32:57.210
But my blood stasis disease
dooms me to a short life.

32:58.390 --> 32:59.790
Grand Tutor Xie's selfish desires

32:59.790 --> 33:01.850
also showed me another, better path.

33:03.350 --> 33:05.410
Yizhi is more suited for that throne.

33:07.880 --> 33:09.920
The mistakes my father made in the past

33:09.920 --> 33:12.240
have always been a hidden danger
to the army's morale.

33:12.240 --> 33:14.040
I had prepared for that long ago.

33:14.590 --> 33:18.310
But I didn't expect the Eagle King
to use the Grand Tutor's life as bait.

33:18.310 --> 33:19.570
Since he made his move,

33:20.110 --> 33:22.880
we might as well uproot the old grievances
once and for all.

33:22.880 --> 33:24.590
So we turned his scheme against him

33:24.590 --> 33:27.160
and staged a fallout
between the ruler and his subject—

33:27.160 --> 33:28.960
paving the way with flesh and blood.

33:28.960 --> 33:30.290
Take this secret report

33:30.790 --> 33:32.050
and read it carefully.

33:40.600 --> 33:41.750
Beware of spies.

33:55.110 --> 33:56.310
I planned everything

33:56.590 --> 33:57.720
and arranged it all.

33:58.720 --> 34:00.180
To achieve the final goal,

34:00.200 --> 34:01.660
I can sacrifice anything.

34:01.720 --> 34:02.980
But the only exception

34:03.310 --> 34:03.880
is you.

34:05.440 --> 34:06.240
I was afraid that if I told you,

34:06.240 --> 34:08.699
I'd lose the courage
to walk this path alone.

34:08.760 --> 34:10.960
But with the fate of the realm
on my shoulders,

34:10.960 --> 34:13.290
I couldn't afford to
cling to my own life."

34:20.360 --> 34:22.510
Xiao Wuyi, you're a liar!

34:23.000 --> 34:23.800
Bastard!

34:24.190 --> 34:24.840
Jerk!

34:24.840 --> 34:26.480
Why didn't you tell me?

34:34.030 --> 34:35.429
When did you two bastards

34:36.000 --> 34:37.280
conspire to send him

34:37.280 --> 34:38.400
to his death?

34:40.440 --> 34:41.400
And that arrow—

34:41.710 --> 34:43.239
whose idea was that really?

34:43.630 --> 34:45.440
That night in the imperial prison,

34:45.440 --> 34:46.400
when you left,

34:47.150 --> 34:48.280
the stab he gave me

34:50.030 --> 34:51.230
was for Feng An to see.

34:51.760 --> 34:52.960
The next time we meet,

34:53.880 --> 34:55.480
there's no need to hold back.

34:58.630 --> 34:59.400
No!

34:59.460 --> 35:00.790
-Xiao Wuyi!
-Kill them!

35:06.510 --> 35:07.280
So,

35:09.670 --> 35:11.150
you told Da to stay put

35:11.150 --> 35:12.670
because, aside from
the Northern Qin spies

35:12.670 --> 35:14.550
who had already been exposed
outside Jiankang Palace,

35:14.550 --> 35:17.750
the one you were really guarding against
was Eunuch Feng?

35:17.920 --> 35:19.400
Not just guarding against him—

35:19.400 --> 35:20.460
you were using him.

35:20.880 --> 35:22.340
You wanted to use his words

35:22.440 --> 35:24.100
to make the Eagle King believe

35:24.190 --> 35:26.070
that even if you knew something was wrong
with the case,

35:26.070 --> 35:27.760
you would still suspect Xiao Wuyi

35:27.760 --> 35:29.290
and force him into a corner?

35:31.960 --> 35:33.020
At least we had him.

35:35.590 --> 35:37.820
What did the miraculous doctor mean
by 2 months?

35:37.820 --> 35:39.480
He's suffered from blood stasis

35:39.480 --> 35:40.540
and taken an arrow.

35:40.960 --> 35:42.360
After that long, rough journey
back to the Northern Border,

35:42.360 --> 35:43.960
things won't go well for him.

35:44.590 --> 35:46.670
But the miraculous doctor's medicine

35:46.670 --> 35:48.670
can only keep him alive for 2 months.

35:53.030 --> 35:54.290
Did it ever occur to you

35:54.640 --> 35:56.900
that he might not return within 2 months?

35:56.920 --> 35:58.590
What if the Eagle King doesn't

35:58.590 --> 36:01.190
fall for your plan
and refuses to take the bait?

36:08.150 --> 36:08.800
Yaoyao.

36:10.230 --> 36:11.430
Don't be mad anymore.

36:13.590 --> 36:14.630
I'm not mad.

36:15.840 --> 36:17.170
I'm just thinking about

36:18.590 --> 36:20.520
how I'm going to bury this bastard.

36:28.700 --> 36:30.100
I have something for you.

36:37.600 --> 36:38.330
This was made

36:38.800 --> 36:40.400
by melting down the Phoenix Heart Token

36:40.400 --> 36:41.860
that Xiao Wuyi cut in half.

36:43.480 --> 36:45.080
He wanted me to give it to you.

36:51.920 --> 36:54.630
This was originally
my mother's Phoenix Imperial Seal.

36:54.630 --> 36:55.780
How about I melt it

36:56.140 --> 36:58.000
and make it into a hairpin for you?

37:04.110 --> 37:07.530
♪ A dying memory glimmers low ♪

37:07.830 --> 37:11.510
♪ You appear, but I can't hold you so ♪

37:11.610 --> 37:15.980
♪ Time itself comes to a sudden halt ♪

37:16.340 --> 37:19.030
♪ So desolate ♪

37:19.610 --> 37:23.280
♪ I traded obsession for this loss ♪

37:22.190 --> 37:23.310
Both Her Highness and I

37:23.310 --> 37:26.850
♪ If I could lay my heart bare and cross ♪

37:24.880 --> 37:27.040
wish for you to live freely and happily.

37:27.040 --> 37:32.370
♪ Would you once more have pity on me ♪

37:30.150 --> 37:31.480
"The road ahead is long,

37:31.760 --> 37:33.010
and I may never return.

37:33.010 --> 37:36.450
♪ If the heavens should change
and fate tear me apart ♪

37:33.710 --> 37:35.170
This is my farewell to you.

37:35.360 --> 37:36.440
I have failed you.

37:36.480 --> 37:40.470
♪ Yet still cannot undo one beat
of my heart's art ♪

37:39.150 --> 37:40.610
I dare not ask for another life together.

37:40.610 --> 37:44.320
♪ I've traveled so far—
the day I find you again ♪

37:41.400 --> 37:44.340
I only wish that in this life,
Yaoyao, you may meet a good man again

37:44.340 --> 37:48.040
♪ I fear you might have forgotten me ♪

37:44.590 --> 37:46.050
and live in peace and joy."

37:48.290 --> 37:51.120
♪ I fear no doom of endless karmic pain ♪

37:51.140 --> 37:52.010
♪ Only that you drift far from my side ♪

37:52.890 --> 37:55.800
[Eagle King's Camp; Northern Qin]

37:59.840 --> 38:03.150
Is His Highness the Eagle King still not
coming out to receive the imperial edict?

38:01.390 --> 38:03.060
[Imperial Envoy of Northern Qin]

38:07.400 --> 38:08.400
Your Excellency,

38:08.760 --> 38:09.820
His Highness is ill

38:10.360 --> 38:12.110
and cannot come out to
receive the edict for the time being.

38:12.110 --> 38:12.970
Preposterous!

38:13.440 --> 38:15.400
Since when does receiving an edict
depend on one's convenience?

38:15.400 --> 38:19.000
The Eagle King should not presume
that being the Emperor's uncle

38:19.030 --> 38:21.280
exempts him from
observing the proper hierarchy.

38:21.280 --> 38:22.320
We wouldn't dare.

38:22.880 --> 38:24.030
His Highness has always

38:24.030 --> 38:26.290
held His Majesty in the highest respect.

38:27.070 --> 38:28.670
Isn't that right, everyone?

38:28.920 --> 38:29.760
Yes!

38:30.440 --> 38:31.670
His Majesty has heard

38:31.760 --> 38:34.920
that the Eagle King brought back
an honored guest from Southern Ye.

38:34.920 --> 38:38.660
His Majesty wishes to invite
this honored guest to visit the Capital.

38:38.660 --> 38:40.190
Here is the imperial edict.

38:40.280 --> 38:41.720
If His Highness the Eagle King

38:41.720 --> 38:44.110
still refuses to come out
to receive the edict,

38:44.110 --> 38:45.110
then I

38:45.840 --> 38:47.500
will have to proclaim it here.

38:48.960 --> 38:49.620
Wait, wait.

38:49.880 --> 38:50.680
My stomach...

38:51.230 --> 38:52.360
Take me to the latrine.

38:52.360 --> 38:55.160
Escort the Imperial Envoy
to the guest residence.

39:01.800 --> 39:02.730
Young Lord Xiao,

39:02.800 --> 39:05.320
what do you suppose my dear nephew,
the Emperor,

39:05.320 --> 39:06.980
wants with you in the Capital?

39:11.030 --> 39:12.760
You're really no fun, you know?

39:13.030 --> 39:14.840
You and I have fought for a decade.

39:14.840 --> 39:17.030
How many decades
does a man get in one lifetime?

39:17.030 --> 39:18.590
That makes us friends of a sort,
doesn't it?

39:18.590 --> 39:19.590
Now that you're on my turf,

39:19.590 --> 39:20.720
you don't even let me

39:21.400 --> 39:22.440
play the gracious host

39:22.440 --> 39:23.840
and treat you to a good meal.

39:23.840 --> 39:26.440
You're refusing even water
on your hunger strike.

39:26.440 --> 39:29.300
It makes me look like
a terribly ill-mannered host.

39:31.000 --> 39:31.510
Fine.

39:32.750 --> 39:33.800
If you won't talk,

39:33.800 --> 39:36.550
I'll go have a chat
with that guard of yours instead.

39:36.550 --> 39:38.810
Her injuries look even worse than yours.

39:38.960 --> 39:41.020
Maybe her temper isn't quite as foul.

39:41.400 --> 39:43.060
Don't waste your breath on me.

39:43.360 --> 39:45.290
Returning to Jiankang was a gamble

39:45.400 --> 39:46.260
I chose to take.

39:47.320 --> 39:48.580
And now that I've lost,

39:49.760 --> 39:50.710
unlike you,

39:51.960 --> 39:54.030
I accept whatever comes—life or death.

39:54.030 --> 39:54.960
Unlike me?

39:55.710 --> 39:57.510
At the Battle of Jiuzhang Plain,

39:58.630 --> 40:01.160
your Black Eagle Army
suffered heavy losses,

40:01.400 --> 40:03.760
and your Empress Dowager
passed away shortly after.

40:03.760 --> 40:05.420
Your biggest support is gone.

40:05.480 --> 40:07.000
The new Emperor has ascended the throne.

40:07.000 --> 40:09.070
You refuse to resign yourself to that
and urgently need a great victory.

40:09.070 --> 40:11.670
But your young Emperor
doesn't want you to win.

40:11.920 --> 40:13.070
That's why he demands you hand me over,

40:13.070 --> 40:14.540
afraid that you and I might join forces.

40:14.540 --> 40:16.190
But have you ever thought about this?

40:16.190 --> 40:18.190
The fact that he moved so quickly

40:19.400 --> 40:20.840
means your own ranks

40:22.070 --> 40:24.070
aren't exactly airtight.

40:27.920 --> 40:28.710
Sure enough,

40:28.890 --> 40:31.190
the one who knows you best
is not your friend,

40:31.190 --> 40:32.190
but your enemy.

40:32.920 --> 40:35.250
Yet aren't you even more foolish
than I am?

40:36.710 --> 40:38.440
Li Mao used you

40:38.440 --> 40:39.640
to secure his throne,

40:39.840 --> 40:42.400
then the moment he had the chance,
he turned on you—

40:42.400 --> 40:44.530
killed your family and took your wife.

40:44.800 --> 40:45.670
How much longer

40:46.280 --> 40:48.680
are you going to tolerate
a ruler like that?

40:49.760 --> 40:50.440
Why not

40:51.710 --> 40:52.840
join forces with me?

40:53.710 --> 40:56.240
Tell me the Beifu Army's
defense strategies.

40:56.400 --> 40:57.880
From Luozhou to Huaixi,

40:58.000 --> 40:59.000
it'll all be

40:59.280 --> 41:01.010
within our grasp in an instant.

41:01.320 --> 41:03.320
We'll divide the realm between us.

41:06.320 --> 41:07.850
My loyalty is to the nation—

41:08.550 --> 41:09.680
not to any one ruler.

41:12.440 --> 41:14.960
Then what if I promise to
help you fight your way back into Jiankang

41:14.960 --> 41:16.550
and snatch Xie Jiayu back?

41:19.760 --> 41:22.220
Then you can personally
cut off Li Mao's head

41:22.510 --> 41:25.510
and offer it in tribute to your family.
How about that?

41:26.960 --> 41:28.620
My days are already numbered.

41:28.960 --> 41:30.070
Wealth and glory,

41:30.960 --> 41:32.550
love and desire,

41:34.070 --> 41:35.130
mean nothing to me.

41:46.360 --> 41:47.560
Who would've thought

41:48.400 --> 41:50.660
that the illustrious Crown Prince Wenxi

41:51.710 --> 41:55.710
would turn out to be such a waste—
handing the realm over to someone else.

41:56.840 --> 41:58.880
H-How did you know that?

41:59.920 --> 42:01.380
If I didn't even know that,

42:01.630 --> 42:04.070
how could I dare play a game
of divide and conquer?

42:04.070 --> 42:05.030
You planted Li Lejun

42:05.030 --> 42:06.190
by my side.

42:07.000 --> 42:09.850
Did you really think I had no one planted
in your Eastern Palace?

42:09.850 --> 42:10.710
Let me tell you.

42:11.360 --> 42:14.670
Li Mao is narrow-minded, indecisive,
and vicious by nature.

42:14.670 --> 42:16.920
Precisely because you're
Crown Prince Wenxi,

42:16.920 --> 42:18.580
he will never truly trust you,

42:18.760 --> 42:21.360
let alone let you command the Beifu Army.

42:22.510 --> 42:24.710
Even if you help him retake the Capital,

42:24.920 --> 42:28.580
you will end up being discarded
when you outlive your usefulness.

42:37.710 --> 42:38.550
Look closely.

42:39.960 --> 42:43.220
This is the armor Emperor Wenxi wore
when he fell in battle.

42:43.960 --> 42:45.800
Back then, he personally led the campaign,

42:45.800 --> 42:47.760
holding off overwhelming enemy forces.

42:47.760 --> 42:49.590
But to his dying breath,
he never saw the reinforcements

42:49.590 --> 42:51.520
from your Southern Ye noble clans.

42:52.920 --> 42:53.920
Is such a realm

42:54.190 --> 42:55.590
still worth protecting?

43:02.280 --> 43:02.800
Oh,

43:03.960 --> 43:05.960
and the day after you left Jiankang,

43:05.960 --> 43:07.220
Li Mao issued a decree:

43:07.360 --> 43:08.670
the Xiao family committed treason,

43:08.670 --> 43:10.190
you were reduced to a commoner,

43:10.190 --> 43:13.850
and every member of the Xiao family
aged 14 and above was beheaded.

43:13.880 --> 43:14.810
On the third day,

43:15.480 --> 43:17.190
another decree came from the palace

43:17.190 --> 43:20.190
that Xie Jiayu was to be taken
as his secondary consort.

43:20.190 --> 43:21.840
Xie resisted to the point of
threatening her own life,

43:21.840 --> 43:24.570
so he had her shackled
inside the Eastern Palace.

43:25.440 --> 43:27.760
The wedding will be held tomorrow.
